com.bmc.arsys.api

Interface ARErrors


  • public interface ARErrors
    The ARErrors class defines all the integer values used by the Java API as errors and warnings as constants. These constants are equivalent to the #define statements found in the arerrno.h file. The message text of the public static final int statements is found in the ar.cat.src file. These constants in this ARErrors class contain the codes for all the errors that can be returned from the AR System server. Refer by number to the Error Messages Guide for the contents of these constants.
